Hash routing
#                               => Application Main Page
#index                          => Application Main Page
#sign_in                        => Application Sign In Page
#register                       => Application Register Page
#app/[module]                   => Module Main Page               (#math)
#app/[module]/index             => Module Main Page               (#math/index)
#app/[module]/learn             => Module Learn Main Page         (#math/learn)
#app/[module]/learn/[page]      => Module Learn Content Page      (#math/learn/chapter1-page1)
#app/[module]/practise          => Module Practise Main Page      (#math/practise)
#app/[module]/practise/[page]   => Module Practise Content Page   (#math/practise/exercise1)